WEBVTT

00:00:00.546 --> 00:00:02.793
Bila sam u New Yorku 
za vrijeme uragana Sandy,

00:00:02.793 --> 00:00:05.033
i jedan mali bijeli pas imena Maui

00:00:05.033 --> 00:00:06.918
je bio sa mnom.

00:00:06.918 --> 00:00:09.390
Pola grada je bilo u mraku 
zbog nestanka struje,

00:00:09.390 --> 00:00:11.614
a ja sam živjela u mračnom dijelu.

00:00:11.614 --> 00:00:13.723
Dakle, 
Maui se bojao mraka,

00:00:13.723 --> 00:00:15.827
pa sam ga morala nositi uza stube,

00:00:15.827 --> 00:00:18.915
zapravo prvo niz stube, 
zbog njegove šetnje

00:00:18.915 --> 00:00:20.803
i onda ga opet vratiti gore.

00:00:20.803 --> 00:00:23.784
Također sam teglila 
litre i litre boca vode

00:00:23.784 --> 00:00:25.883
na sedmi kat svaki dan.

00:00:25.883 --> 00:00:27.456
I kroz sve to,

00:00:27.456 --> 00:00:29.760
morala sam držati svjetiljku među zubima.

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:32.404
Trgovine u blizini 
bile su bez džepnih svjetiljki,